Introducing new nations could also be a good way to group champions unaffiliated with the current regions however  this will likely be nations mentioned before
For instance kumungu jungle , which is still canon, can group together a bunch of the jungle champions such as {{champion:143}} {{champion:76}} {{champion:150}} {{champion:121}} {{champion:107}}  
And I think an arcane based nation would be difficult to just pop up in the lore unless it was hidden, from world causes nation of that importance can't just come out of nowhere
